<p>There are a number of errors in <xref rid="pntd.0003786.t001" ref-type="table">Table 3</xref>. The table legend should read: Breakdown of economic costs of rabies by cluster in millions of USD. The headings for columns six, seven, and eight are incorrect. They should be in the following order: Dog vaccination, Dog population management, Livestock losses. Please see the correct <xref rid="pntd.0003786.t001" ref-type="table">Table 3</xref> below.</p>
